  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Creating a Hedging Area</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page task  - topic-topic task-task \" id=\"loio936d5758eab99344e10000000a4450e5\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Creating a Hedging Area</h1><div class=\"body taskbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\"></p><section class=\"section procedure\"><span id=\"steps\" class=\"anchor\"></span><div class=\"ol steps tasklabel\"><h2 class=\"sectiontitle tasklabel\">Procedure</h2></div><ol class=\"ol steps\"><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">Call the function from the area menu under <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Treasury and Risk Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hedge Management and Accounting</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hedge Management</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Master Data </span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Define Hedging Areas</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph sap-technical-name sap-technical-name\">TOE_HEDGING_AREA</span>).</span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">Enter an ID for the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Hedging Area</span> (not exceeding six digits) and choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Create</span>.</span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">In the dialog box that appears, enter an explanatory description for the hedging area and enter the valid-from date of the hedging area.</span><div class=\"itemgroup info\"><p class=\"p\">Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Create</span>.</p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">The version number of this new hedging area is set to 1.</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">You can use another hedging area version as a template for the first version of the new hedging area.</p></li></ul></aside></div></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">Enter the valid-from date for the hedging area version.</span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">In the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Memo</span> area, you can enter a free text containing additional information for this hedging area version.</span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"afe73d5881129244e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Main Data</a></span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"618b3d58eaa89144e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area Tab: General Data</a></span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"046c5358bae84442e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Currencies</a></span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"ca6c5358bae84442e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Filters for Exposures</a></span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"7b6d5358bae84442e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Filters for Hedges</a></span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"e26e5358bae84442e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area:\nTarget Quotas</a></span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"caa13e6a08244e0a82f120885e166687.html\" title=\"On this tab, you enter the master data relevant for the automated creation of FX hedge requests.\">Hedging Area: FX Hedge Request</a></span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"6a8f3d58eaa89144e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Hedge\nAccounting I</a></span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\">\n<span class=\"ph cmd\"><a class=\"xref\" href=\"b28e3d58eaa89144e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Hedge\nAccounting II</a></span>\n</li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">If you have made the necessary settings for target quotas on the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Main Data</span> tab to enable the entry of target quotas, you can enter the target quotas in the target quota tables on the <a class=\"xref\" href=\"e26e5358bae84442e10000000a4450e5.html\">Hedging Area: Target Quotas</a> tab.</span></li><li class=\"li step stepexpand\"><span class=\"ph cmd\">Save your entries.</span></li></ol></section></div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}